Oldendorf can also refer to: *Dr. [[William H. Oldendorf]], an American neurologist and pioneer in neuroimaging *Admiral [[Jesse B. Oldendorf]], a US Navy task force commander in the 7th Fleet, during World War 2 {{Disambig}}

