'''Paulus Modestus Schücking''' (''Paul Nicolaus Bernhard Joseph Schücking, genannt Modestus'' - 16 June 1787, [[Münster]] - 16 June 1867, [[Bremen]]) was a German lawyer, councillor, philosopher and writer. He is also notable as the husband of [[Katharina Sibylla Schücking]] and the father of [[Levin Schücking]].

