'''Ælfric''' ({{lang-ang|Ælfrīc}}; died ''[[circa|c.]]'' 960) was a medieval [[Bishop of Hereford]]. He was [[consecrated]] in either 934 or between 937 and 940 and died either between 949 and 958 or in 971.<ref name=Handbook217>Fryde, et al. ''Handbook of British Chronology'' p. 217</ref>

