'''Marie Plosjö''' (born 1976) is a [[Swedish people|Swedish]] [[Model (person)|model]] for magazines such as ''Cafe'', ''Moore'' and ''[[Slitz]]''.<ref>{{cite web|author=Tony Kollberg |url=http://www.kollbergmedia.se/simmagazine/simexpo/visabild.asp?m=1 |title=:: [ S i m M a g a z i n e © - Din nöjesplats på nätet! &#93; :: |publisher=Kollbergmedia.se |date= |accessdate=2012-08-08}}</ref> She has also been in ''[[Playboy]]'' as well as ''ICE'' magazines. She has posed for some pictures which may be classified as nudes.<ref>[http://www.jesper.nu/bilder/tjejer/marie_plosjo ]{{dead link|date=August 2012}}</ref> In 2005 she was a contestant in season 2 of the reality show ''[[Paradise Hotel]]'' where she ended up in a fight over [[David Lotfi]] with her former friend and also model [[Natacha Peyre]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/vss/noje/story/0,2789,719659,00.html |title=Marie hotas i sexdramat &#124; Dokusåpa &#124; TV &#124; Nöjesbladet &#124; Aftonbladet |publisher=Aftonbladet.se |date=2005-10-26 |accessdate=2012-08-08}}</ref> Marie Plosjö has also released a single called "Boom boom boom". In 2008 she continued her modelling career, and was host for the final of [[Miss World Sweden]] 2007 and 2008. She is CEO of a big blogportal in Sweden,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mondoblog.se/ |title=Mondoblog |publisher=Mondoblog.se |date=2012-02-10 |accessdate=2012-08-08}}</ref> and she is an artist with exhibitions around the world.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theartofmarieplosjo.com |title=The ART of Marie Plosjö |publisher=Theartofmarieplosjo.com |date= |accessdate=2012-08-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mondoblog.se/marieplosjo/kategori/konst |title=Konstsida &#124; Marie Plosjö |publisher=Mondoblog.se |date=2012-03-21 |accessdate=2012-08-08}}</ref>
